Description: 99 Digital marketing agency : Empowering Brands with Strategic Marketing
Headquarters Regions: Greater New York Area, East Coast, Northeastern US
Full Description: 99 Digital marketing agency is a leading digital marketing agency committed to helping businesses thrive in the fast-paced and ever-evolving digital landscape. With our expertise, creativity, and data-driven approach, we empower brands to connect with their target audience, build a strong online presence, and achieve measurable results. At 99 Digital marketing agency, we understand that in today's digital era, a strong online presence is essential for business success. Our team of seasoned digital marketing professionals possesses a deep understanding of various digital channels, from search engine optimization (SEO) and social media marketing to content creation and email campaigns. We leverage this expertise to craft customized, comprehensive digital marketing strategies tailored to our clients' unique goals and objectives. Our agency places a strong emphasis on collaboration and partnership. We believe that successful digital marketing is a result of combining our industry knowledge with our clients' expertise in their respective fields. Through close collaboration, we gain a deep understanding of our clients' brand values, target audience, and business objectives. This allows us to create impactful and personalized digital marketing campaigns that deliver exceptional results. What sets us apart is our data-driven approach. We believe in the power of analytics and continuously monitor, analyze, and optimize our clients' campaigns to maximize their return on investment (ROI). Our team employs advanced analytics tools and techniques to measure key performance indicators (KPIs), track conversions, and identify opportunities for improvement. By analyzing data and making data-driven decisions, we ensure that our clients' digital marketing efforts yield tangible results and drive growth. Our comprehensive suite of services includes: Search Engine Optimization (SEO): Enhancing website visibility and organic traffic through keyword optimization, technical SEO, and content strategy. Social Media Marketing: Building and managing engaging social media campaigns across platforms to foster brand awareness, engagement, and community growth. Content Creation and Marketing: Crafting compelling and valuable content, including blog posts, articles, videos, and infographics, to drive brand authority, engage audiences, and enhance SEO. Pay-Per-Click Advertising (PPC): Implementing targeted and strategic PPC campaigns on search engines and social media platforms to drive qualified traffic and conversions. Email Marketing: Developing personalized email campaigns to nurture leads, foster customer loyalty, and drive conversions. Conversion Rate Optimization (CRO): Analyzing user behavior, conducting A/B testing, and optimizing landing pages and user flows to maximize conversions and improve website performance. Analytics and Reporting: Providing comprehensive data analysis, regular performance reports, and actionable insights to measure campaign success and inform future strategies. 99 Digital marketing agency is dedicated to delivering exceptional results

Description: PERSONALRIA (PR) is a platform that replaces mutual funds as the primary investment vehicle available to retail investors.
Headquarters Regions: West Coast, Western US
Full Description: PERSONALRIA (PR) is a platform that replaces mutual funds as the primary investment vehicle available to retail investors. There are two key participants in the platform: REGISTERED INVESTMENT ADVISORS (RIAs), and retail investors (investors with an average, or below average, amount of investible assets). RIAs are investment professionals that usually cater to the high-net-worth market segment. Their technological capabilities will enable the creation of virtual funds managed by registered investment advisors (RIAs). That is, each real-money portfolio managed directly by one of their RIAs can be set to continuously trigger, on a proportionate basis, an identical portfolio in their clients' brokerage accounts. The web-app suite will enable the creation of investment vehicles wrapped in layers of the much needed transparency and interactivity features. RIAs will now profitably engage with the retail investor market segment, and retail investors will have access to a much improved level of investment talent.
